{"tid":1858008,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支持醫護 封關救港","createTime":"2020-02-02T12:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T17:37:32.000Z","uid":322412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00462aa8f80a27d8e7c80fe6a2388fa1f5fb0401","tid":1858008,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"📢民主黨發起全港簽名運動<br />\n支持醫護 封關救港 禁止內地人來港<br />\n<br />\n✅ 網上聯署連結: shorturl.at/iHSVZ<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，內地確診個案已經突破一萬大關，全中國擴散，香港亦已經超過14個確診個案。封關是阻止疫情擴散的重中之重的必須手段。<br />\n<br />\n內地患者源源不絕來港求醫，醫療系統無可能應付全國需求。林鄭拒封關，醫護系統爆煲，香港人人自危。醫護人員發動罷工要求封關，是保護港人下迫於無奈的一步。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們要求政府：<br />\n<br />\n1. 支持醫護人員訴求，即時封關，於關口採取嚴厲管制入境措施，禁止內地人來港；及<br />\n<br />\n2. 提供足夠口罩及防護裝備給醫護人員，前線公務員及市民，並制訂措施禁止商人抬價。<br />\n#民主黨 #撐醫護 #罷工 #封關 #聯署 #林卓延"},{"pid":"78294d2524d2e941bdfd2c4485deaec8e1032045","tid":1858008,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d2e4a60087eb49b8c133d00bd1053bf7ee2be23","tid":1858008,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"罷工人數調查<br />\nPWH <br />\n7A ~7<br />\n7B ~17<br />\n10C ~10 +10ccu 8<br />\n11A ~17<br />\n11C ～16<br />\n12B ~ 14<br />\n10LM ~20<br />\nNNU: 73<br />\n11HKLM: 23<br />\n4Eonco:~7<br />\nCIC~5<br />\n<br />\nPrivate: ~17<br />\n<br />\nolmh E3：～10<br />\n<br />\nUch <br />\n10B: ~12<br />\n12B: ~14<br />\nUCH Physio: 40<br />\n<br />\nPY ICU: ~33<br />\n<br />\nYCH<br />\nOT: 24<br />\nTSSU: 6<br />\n<br />\nKWH<br />\nE4 12<br />\nN3 18<br />\nN4 27<br />\nE2 3<br />\nSurg 10<br />\nE10 may SL<br />\nE8 6-7<br />\nN8 7<br />\nN11 10<br />\nO&amp;G 17<br />\nOT 40<br />\nICU 6<br />\n<br />\nCmc <br />\n5D 11<br />\n13B 19<br />\n11B 18<br />\n2A 3<br />\n5C 2<br />\n13A 18<br />\n12A 11<br />\nOT 38<br />\n9AB 14<br />\n<br />\nPMH<br />\nOT 33<br />\n<br />\nQEH<br />\nO&amp;T ~29<br />\n<br />\nPOH <br />\nOT 24<br />\n4s 10<br />\n4n 10<br />\n5s 11<br />\n5